---
import HeadingRule from '../../HeadingRule.astro'
---

<section class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32'>

  <!-- Subtle grid texture -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>

  <!-- Giant Titan One watermark -->
  <div class="font-heading pointer-events-none absolute -left-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none leading-none"
    aria-hidden='true'>
    €€€
  </div>

  <!-- Orange corner accent right -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-1.5 h-40 bg-sage rounded-l-full'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>

  <!-- Top hairline -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-teal/15 to-transparent'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>
  <!-- Bottom hairline -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-teal/15 to-transparent'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>

  <div class='relative container-site'>

    <!-- ── Section header ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class='mb-16 md:mb-20 max-w-3xl'>
      <div data-animate class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-8'>
        <span class='block h-px w-10 bg-sage' aria-hidden='true'></span>
        <h2 class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-sage'>
          Lo que me comprometo a hacer
        </h2>
      </div>

      <p
        data-animate

        class='leading-[0.92] tracking-tight mb-6'>
        <span class='block font-heading text-h2 font-bold leading-[1.05] text-cream/60'>
          Tienes que ganar
        </span>
        <span class='block font-heading text-h2 font-bold leading-[1.05] text-cream'>
          más de lo que me pagas<span class='text-sage'>.</span>
        </span>
      </p>

      <HeadingRule color='var(--color-sage)' fadeColor='var(--color-teal)' data-animate />

      <p data-animate class='mt-6 text-base text-cream/70 leading-relaxed text-pretty max-w-[52ch]'>
        Si me contratas, lo primero que hacemos juntos es calcular
        <strong class='font-semibold text-cream'>cuánto dinero tiene que entrar por los clientes que te llegan desde Google</strong>.
        Si lo que me pagas no trae más de lo que cuesta, no tiene ningún sentido seguir.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
